appStages.name: Introduction
appStages.stageDetails:
{ "components": [ { "label": "HTML", "attrs": [ { "attr": "", "value": "" } ], "content": "

QA Test Case Assistant

Overview

This assistant generates comprehensive QA test cases from natural language feature descriptions or requirement documents. It is designed to assist QA teams in accelerating test planning with structured, ready-to-use test cases.

Key Features

  • + SRS to test case conversion
    • + Requirement-to-test mapping
      • + Identification of edge cases and negative scenarios
      • + Consistent test case format with traceability

Key Insights

The assistant generates structured test cases with:

  • + Unique test case identifiers
    • + Step-by-step test instructions
    • + Pre-conditions and expected results
    • + Linkage to related functional requirements
